com.ubudu.indoorlocation

Class UbuduPositionUpdate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ubudu.indoorlocation.UbuduPositionUpdate

  • public class UbuduPositionUpdate
extends java.lang.Object
    Class describing a position update. It contains information about raw estimated position, smoothed position and closest navigable point. It also contains information about closest beacon and closest zone. This object is always an argument of the event handled by Indoor Location delegate.
